Annihilator got blown away by your shot Tritan, he's no longer in the 
vicinity.

::Prowl::

A look of surprise crosses Prowl's face as he hears Iron Raptor apologise. It 
was a battle, and mistakes happen in battles.

He puts his hand under Iron Raptor's chin and makes her look into his eyes.

"That's quite allright," he says, "Mistakes happen."

He suddenly grins, standing up, "But remind me never to piss you off."

He smiles at her and transforms into beast mode. He looks at where Tritan 
flew off to. He needs to thank the bot later.

He turns to look back at Iron Raptor. "Lets get back to base."
